jobs_results.description:
We are looking for a highly motivated App Developer to collaborate with our team on various projects. As an iOS Developer, you will be working in a fast-paced and dynamic environment, delivering high-quality results under tight deadlines.

The ideal candidate should have experience in developing mobile apps for iOS using UIKit and SwiftUI, as well as knowledge of Apple frameworks such as ARKit or CoreML. Additionally, expertise in concurrent code development, API integrations, Test Driven Development, and Agile Methodologies is required.

The position requires strong programming skills in Swift, optionally including other languages like Objective-C or Python. Experience in developing user interfaces with SwiftUI and UIKit, as well as advanced Apple Frameworks, is essential.

Key responsibilities include:
• Developing high-quality iOS apps using modern design patterns and scalable software architecture;
• Collaborating with cross-functional teams to meet project goals and deadlines;
• Contributing to the development of server-side applications and database management systems;
• Participating in Test Driven Development and Agile Methodologies.

We offer a competitive salary range of €65,000 - €90,000 per year, depending on experience, plus additional benefits.

To be successful in this role, you should have:
• 1+ year of experience as an App Developer for iOS within a team of developers;
• Professional or personal experience collaborating with diverse groups of people;
• Excellent verbal and written communication, as well as presentation skills;
• Proficiency in English (C1 or C2 level).

Please submit your CV and relevant portfolio for consideration. We look forward to hearing from you!
